src=\&quot;https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-b2dd1e0b67913c71c52add763acf70e3_b.jpg\&quot; data-caption=\&quot;\&quot; data-size=\&quot;normal\&quot; data-rawwidth=\&quot;640\&quot; data-rawheight=\&quot;851\&quot; class=\&quot;origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\&quot; width=\&quot;640\&quot; data-original=\&quot;https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-b2dd1e0b67913c71c52add763acf70e3_r.jpg\&quot;&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;&lt;p&gt;书房要满足两个人同时办公的安排，地板上的插座，桌面上的电源盒都源于简洁实用&lt;/p&gt;&lt;figure&gt;&lt;img src=\&quot;https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-b9ae9bc10e2040b5e9e8a69af65f5cbc_b.jpg\&quot; data-caption=\&quot;\&quot; data-size=\&quot;normal\&quot; data-rawwidth=\&quot;640\&quot; data-rawheight=\&quot;481\&quot; class=\&quot;origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\&quot; width=\&quot;640\&quot; data-original=\&quot;https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-b9ae9bc10e2040b5e9e8a69af65f5cbc_r.jpg\&quot;&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;书桌尺寸2米*0.8米，为罗胖桌改款，中间为下沉电源盒&lt;/p&gt;&lt;figure&gt;&lt;img src=\&quot;https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-1c6ae94b1674cea3f5cd6414d9dd8855_b.jpg\&quot; data-caption=\&quot;\&quot; data-size=\&quot;normal\&quot; data-rawwidth=\&quot;640\&quot; data-rawheight=\&quot;851\&quot; class=\&quot;origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\&quot; width=\&quot;640\&quot; data-original=\&quot;https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-1c6ae94b1674cea3f5cd6414d9dd8855_r.jpg\&quot;&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;&lt;p&gt;下沉电源盒&lt;/p&gt;&lt;figure&gt;&lt;img src=\&quot;https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-18629608046ad1cdeff478ec5fc762ca_b.jpg\&quot; data-caption=\&quot;\&quot; data-size=\&quot;normal\&quot; data-rawwidth=\&quot;640\&quot; data-rawheight=\&quot;481\&quot; class=\&quot;origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\&quot; width=\&quot;640\&quot; data-original=\&quot;https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-18629608046ad1cdeff478ec5fc762ca_r.jpg\&quot;&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;&lt;p&gt;电池盒两旁为两个实用小抽屉&lt;/p&gt;&lt;figure&gt;&lt;img src=\&quot;https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-b2dd1e0b67913c71c52add763acf70e3_b.jpg\&quot; data-caption=\&quot;\&quot; data-size=\&quot;normal\&quot; data-rawwidth=\&quot;640\&quot